snippet.title: Knockout City Season 7: Mutant Mutiny! Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Deep under the streets of Knockout City, a new kind of brawler is bubbling to the surface. What started as a rumor of glowing eyes, squishy footsteps, and muffled snarls from sewer grates is growing into a revolution of massive proportions. The Mutant Mutiny is here for justice!

The Heroes in a Half Shell have come to Knockout City! Become all four tubular Turtles and score their radical Poses with The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Bundle! That's Turtle Power, baby!

Read on for the latest goop on everything coming in Season 7, including the brand new map, Sludge Works: https://www.knockoutcity.com/updates/knockout-city-season-7-mutant-mutiny 

Take up the fight with Neon, Leonardo, and the rest in Knockout City, when Mutant Mutiny sees daylight on August 30th.
